馬洛達指有可否引入維度<br />
<br />
&quot;Vidal would satisfy all of us. He is an important player, a world class player. Conte and I have a friendly relationship dating back to our great times together. We think highly of him, and it's no mistake they call him the warrior. We are thinking about him, and it's possible because we are suffering in midfield. We have a restricted squad in relation to the competitions we are taking part in.&quot;

干地都讚好<br />
<br />
&quot;Vidal? I can speak about him because I had the pleasure to coach him when he wasn't Vidal yet. When he came to Juve he wasn't the player we know. We worked three years together and he always given everything.&quot;
